<doc id="782104" wikidata="Q1317207" url="?curid=782104" title="Ken Narita">
<text>is a Japanese actor, voice actor and narrator. His real name is . He is currently a freelancer.

He played Sesshomaru in &quot;Inuyasha&quot;, and after Hirotaka Suzuoki&#x27;s death, he took over the roles of Bright Noa and Saitō Hajime.

